Shared Folders between Host & Virtual Machine:

-please refer to Desktop/README/Documentation/Virtual_Machine_Related/Installing_Virtual_Machine_and_Shared_Folder.pdf (section 4) to setup a shared folder.
-shared folder on windows host machine must be named "vboxshare".


*** --------------

-IMPORTANT --- each login will require a reconnection between the host & virtual machine shared folders. MUST ENTER COMMAND BELOW to reconnect folders.

-open terminal & type: 
sudo mount -t vboxsf -o uid=1000,gid=1000 vboxshare /media/sf_vboxshare

*** --------------

-on linux host the shared folder will be located at: /media/sf_vboxshare


